Title: Fix perf data not sent to Carbon if no state is selected
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1648639708
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0i1

After Werk 12704, if none of "State", "Acknowledged", or "Scheduled
downtime depth" was selected in the rule, then no performance data
was sent to the Graphite/InfluxDB connection.
